plot: Day one at the Jersey Shore is off to a wild start when the Gorgas' luau takes a turn for the worse. Rachel drops an arsenal of gossip, angering Marge. Frank struggles with hurt feelings over Dolores' new boundaries. While Teresa and Louie struggle seeing eye to eye on the wedding invite list, Jennifer and Bill continue brushing marital issues under the rug. John Fuda officially joins the Jersey brotherhood. Danielle reaches her breaking point when accusations about her family circulate throughout the party.—Anonymous
